---

{% from "components/slovensko-rodne-cislo-view/macro.njk" import slovenskoRodneCisloView %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<dl>
  <dt>Slovak Personal Number</dt>
  <dd>{{ slovenskoRodneCisloView({ value: "sample-value", label: "Slovak Personal Number" }) }}</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>10 digits in the form YYMMDDCCCX where MM is 01-12 for males and 51-62 for females; X is a check digit and the whole number is divisible by 11.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_identification_number#Slovakia">Slovak Personal Number</a>.</p>
